de.rwth.i2.attestor.phases.counterexamples.counterexampleGeneration.heapConfigurationPair

Class HeapConfigurationPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.phases.counterexamples.counterexampleGeneration.heapConfigurationPair.HeapConfigurationPair
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HeapConfiguration, Graph

    public final class HeapConfigurationPair
extends Object
implements HeapConfiguration, Graph
    A HeapConfigurationPair actually consists of two heap configurations that are materialized together. All methodExecution except for hyperedge replacement are only applied to the actual HeapConfiguration and not to its pairedHeapConfiguration
    Author:
    Christoph
